# Anime Library Directory

Place your anime folders here with the following structure:

anime-library/
├── [Anime Name]/
│   ├── Season 1/ (optional)
│   ├── Season 2/ (optional)
│   ├── Episode 01.mkv
│   ├── Episode 02.mkv
│   └── ...
└── [Another Anime]/
    └── episodes...

The folder names should match or be close to the anime titles on MyAnimeList for best results.
